or this call are:</p><p>LOT 1</p><ul level=\"0\"><li> <p>Digital education and digital competences</p> </li><li> <p>Teaching and teachers</p> </li> </ul><p>LOT 2</p><ul level=\"0\"><li> <p>Funding mechanisms for upskilling and reskilling, including schemes similar to Individual Learning Accounts</p> </li><li> <p>Policy and processes to support the validation of non-formal and informal learning, including through effective guidance</p> </li> </ul><p>The submission and selection of proposals is divided in two stages: pre-proposal stage and full proposal stage.</p>\n", "latestInfos": [{"approvalDate": "Apr 15, 2020 10:35:04 AM", "lastChangeDate": "Apr 15, 2020 10:35:04 AM", "content": "<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><font color=\"#000024\">A</font>s a result of the difficulties by applicants due to the COVID-19 outbreak, we have extended the deadline for the Policy Experimentation.&nbsp; The new deadline is <u>05 May 2020 at 5pm.</u></p>\r\n<p>The evaluation period for pre-proposals : May - June 2020.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}, {"approvalDate": "Dec 10, 2019 10:30:00 AM", "lastChangeDate": "Dec 10, 2019 10:30:00 AM", "content": "The submission session is now available for: EPP-PI-POLICY-2020(EPLUS)"}], "hasForthcomingTopics": false, "hasOpenTopics": false, "allClosedTopics": true}}}